1.40 w 48.00 770.00 m 547.00 770.00 l S
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 746.00 Tm (The repository already implements a substantial end-to-end commerce flow with real) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 731.00 Tm (authentication, persistence, and payment hooks. From an evaluation perspective, the project is) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 716.00 Tm (strong on breadth and user-facing functionality, but the automated quality section shows) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 701.00 Tm (maintainability issues that should be addressed before treating the codebase as production-) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 686.00 Tm (ready.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 663.00 Tm (- Strength: complete customer journey across catalog, cart, account, checkout, and order) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 641.00 Tm (  retrieval.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 619.00 Tm (- Strength: coherent backend route structure with Mongoose models and protected APIs.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 597.00 Tm (- Risk: lint failures indicate code quality and React rule compliance debt.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 575.00 Tm (- Risk: large frontend bundle may affect performance on slower connections.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 553.00 Tm (- Recommendation: add a real automated test suite covering authentication flows, cart logic,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 531.00 Tm (  checkout paths, and API controllers.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 509.00 Tm (- Recommendation: introduce route-level code splitting, fix lint configuration for backend) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 487.00 Tm (  globals, and refactor effect-driven state updates.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 455.00 Tm (End of report.) Tj ET
